text: Diggah Yalli moominiinik ken nafsittee kee ken maalu xaamiteh diggah wohut usun Jannat loonumuh, Yallih diini fayya hoonuh kay gital qeb abaana, tokkel usun koros qidaanaah koros ken qiddah, Yalli wohuh nummâ xaganah ken xagnise Tawraataay, Injiil kee Qhuraan addal, isih haysite xagnih duudusiyyah Yallak iyyi yayseeh? Num mayaysa.Toysa moominiiney sinni tellemmoy Yallâ luk abteenit ayti-kibbi hayisaay teetit wallita, woo tellemo is kaxxa maffaafak
